fulltitle: John Stockwell: The CIA in Nicaragua
title: John Stockwell: The CIA in Nicaragua
description: From 1987, on CIA activities in Central America. Fidel Castro's government is discussed, along with CIA wars on Cuba, Nicaragua and more.
